Trump regularly answers questions when leaving the White House or attending open-ended events or press conferences with visiting dignitaries.
Performing alone at a press conference is rare.
This week in New York, the President may have pointed out the reason for this by appearing uninhibited and at times strangely to the journalists gathered at the scene.
